Package com.db4o.io

Class PagingMemoryStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.db4o.io.PagingMemoryStorage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Storage
    public class PagingMemoryStorage
extends java.lang.Object
implements Storage
    Storage implementation that produces Bin instances that operate in memory. Use this Storage to work with db4o as an in-memory database.
